OL,3,CWho is York and North Yorkshire's
OL,4,Cfirst mayor?
OL,6,FAs mayor, Mr Skaith will be paid
OL,7,F#81,300 a year and will have power
OL,8,Fover decisions on issues including
OL,9,Fpublic transport, housing and adult
OL,10,Feducation.
OL,12,FBut what do we know about David Skaith?
OL,14,FThe 35-year-old was born and raised in
OL,15,FHarrogate, where his brother is a
OL,16,Fpolice officer. He joined the Labour
OL,17,Fparty in 2015.
OL,19,FA keen cricketer, he went on to study
OL,20,Fsport at York St John University.
