OL,6,FWhat were David Skaith's campaign
OL,7,Fpledges?
OL,9,FMr Skaith promised to deliver a cost
OL,10,Fof living recovery plan.
OL,12,FHe said he would fight for more GP and
OL,13,Fdentist appointments and tackle crime
OL,14,Fand antisocial behaviour
OL,16,FHe also pledged to connect communities
OL,17,Fwith a new transport system.
