OL,3,CWho is York and North Yorkshire's
OL,4,Cfirst mayor?
OL,6,FHe moved to Brighton after university,
OL,7,Fbefore returning to North Yorkshire to
OL,8,Fstart menswear store Winston's of
OL,9,FYork, which he has run for nearly a
OL,10,Fdecade.
OL,12,FHe said he would draw on his "business
OL,13,Fexperience" in his new role.
OL,15,F"I am here to work for York and North
OL,16,FYorkshire," he said. "We want change.
OL,17,FWe want people coming in to politics
OL,18,Fand not necessarily from traditional
OL,19,Fbackgrounds I am a small business
OL,20,Fowner with a young family and I will
OL,21,Fbe using that."
