OL,3,CWho is York and North Yorkshire's
OL,4,Cfirst mayor?
OL,6,FMr Skaith said he decided to get
OL,7,Finvolved in politics after his father
OL,8,Fdied during the Covid pandemic.
OL,10,F"I want to grow this region. It's
OL,11,Fabout the people and communities
OL,12,Fhere," he said.
OL,14,F"It's about York and North Yorkshire
OL,15,Fand putting those places on the map."
OL,17,FMr Skaith is married and lives just
OL,18,Foutside York, with his wife Alice and
OL,19,Ftwo children, who he says he wants to
OL,20,F"grow up in a North Yorkshire that is
OL,21,Ffull of opportunity".
